","text":"我们伟大的领袖毛主席万岁！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2f80321112"},{"id":"78fed1967b","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2f80321112"},{"id":"e17bd6c869","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命派联合起来！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2f80321112"},{"id":"87c2b35265","type":"paragraph","text":"向党内走资本主义道路的当权派夺权！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2f80321112"}],"page":{"id":"d45255522a","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2f80321112","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}